[48;2;43;48;59m[39m  115, 115[0m:[39m[48;2;43;48;59m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mAmazon Bedrock for LLM access.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m Bedrock provides managed access to foundation models (Claude, Llama, Titan, and others) without managing infrastructure. For healthcare, the key advantages are: models run within your AWS account boundary, data is not used for model training, and Bedrock is on the HIPAA eligible services list with a signed BAA. You get API access to multiple model families and can switch between them without changing your application code.[K
